creator: Thomas Royer Interactive
descriptionHtml:
Petanque is a game of skill in which you must throw your balls as close to the target as possible.

To play the game, touch the court to reveal a viewfinder which will allow you to adjust your throw.

Then, release your finger to throw your ball onto the court.

You can choose to shoot or point. Official rules are followed, though you only need seven points to win instead of the usual thirteen.

There are two modes to play in:

-Single Player Mode allows you to train by playing against the “computer” so that your aim will improve. (Each level that you win helps you to progress.)

-Multiplayer Mode allows you to play against another player in real time. You will be brought to a menu where you can choose to start a new game or join an existing game.
descriptionShort: Do you shoot or do you point?

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
-Improvement of local multiplayer
-Bugfix
